    "name": "Oasis | Show Full Video, Clean Interface",
    "description": "To watch the full videos on Oasis, use this CSS style, <b>AND disable JavaScript for oasis.weibo.cn </b>\r\n\r\nThere are also options to display or hide other elements of the page, such as:\r\n<ul> <li>the \"Open in App\" button, </li>\r\n<li>the Oasis header at the top, </li>\r\n<li>and the recommended posts below the video post.</li></ul>\r\n(The \"Open in App\" Button is hidden by default.)",
